               <msContents>
                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-6r: Private prayers offered by one አስበሮም (a man, baptismal name ሰበነ ጊዮርጊስ), (apparently his wife, ዕሤተ ማርያም, is often mentioned secondarily above his name), to Mary on behalf of his family, etc. F<locus target="#7r">7r, </locus>-15r: A Collection of Prayers and Supplications under the title, ስብሐተ ፍቁር, arranged by the 318 Orthodox Fathers, to give counsel to people facing problems. F<locus target="#15r">15r, </locus>-17v: Praise of the Beloved in Honor of Mary, ስብሐተ፡ ፍቁር፡. F<locus target="#17v">17v, </locus>-18v: Image of Mary’s Assumption, መልክአ፡ ፍልሰታ፡ ለማርያም፡. Répertoire 213. F<locus target="#18v">18v, </locus>-20r: Image of Mary, incipit: ሰላም: ለዝክረ: ስምኪ: አምሳለ: ስቴ: ወይን: መጥለለ: . . ., Répertoire 177. EMIP 499. F<locus target="#20r">20r, </locus>-25r: Image of Mary, Mälk‘a Maryam, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡, Répertoire 220; MG 735ff.; Incipit: ሰላም ሰላም ለዝክረ ስምኪ ሐዋዝ።  F<locus target="#25r">25r, </locus>-26r: Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace,” እሴብሕ: ጸጋኪ: ማርያም: ወእስእለኪ፡. Not listed in Répertoire ; cf. EMIP 203; cp. Chaine 343. F<locus target="#26rv">26rv, </locus>. Image of Samuel, Not in Répertoire  . Incipit ሰላም ላከ ማኅፈደ መንፈስ አዚዝ። F<locus target="#26v">26v, </locus>-27r: Image of Qirqos, መልክአ፡ ቂርቆስ፡. Incipit: ሰላም ለከ ቂርቆስ ሕፃን። Not in Répertoire. F<locus target="#27r">27r, </locus>-28r: Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace, Clothed in Golden Dress” Répertoire 345. EMIP 733. Incipit : እሴብሕ ጸጋኪ ኦዑጽፍተ ልብሰ ወርቅ. F<locus target="#28r">28r, </locus>: Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace, O My Lady Mary, Fruitful Tree.” Incipit:  እሴብሕ: ጸጋኪ: ኦእግዝእትየ: ማርያም: ዕፅ: ልምሉምት፡. Not listed in Répertoire ; EMIP 701. <locus target="#28v">28v</locus>: Hymn to Mary, “I Praise Thy Grace, O My Lady Mary, Who Makes Me Grow like my Mother. Not listed in Répertoire </summary>
